# YogaBuddy Landing Page Setup

The goal is to create a modern, high-conversion landing page for YogaBuddy and deploy it to GitHub Pages. This page will serve as the first impression for users, showcasing the app's real-time pose detection, AI feedback, and meditation features.

## Proposed Changes

### Assets
#### [NEW] [hero_image.png](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/Yogabuddy-backup-original/hero_image.png)
- A high-quality, AI-generated image of a person practicing yoga in a serene environment with subtle tech overlays.

### Core Landing Page
#### [NEW] [index.html](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/Yogabuddy-backup-original/index.html)
- Main landing page with a sleek, glassmorphic design.
- Features sections: Hero, Features (real-time feedback, pose detection), Meditation, and Call to Action.
#### [NEW] [index.css](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/Yogabuddy-backup-original/index.css)
- Custom CSS using modern design tokens, gradients, and animations.

## Verification Plan

