- View the [index.html](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/Yogabuddy-backup-original/one-breath-app/index.html) file in a browser to ensure all animations, layouts, and assets load correctly.
- Test responsiveness across different screen sizes (mobile/tablet/desktop).
- Verify that links correctly point to the app and GitHub.

